name: Black Tokeez
description:
Tokeez is the world’s first and only multi functional water pipe accessory. With Tokeez, when you want to smoke. . . you smoke. No frantic searching for your lighter or your stash. You will have everything all in one place and ready to go.

	Not just a lighter holder for your water pipe, Tokeez will transform the way you smoke. The once dangerous task of passing both the pipe and lighter will become a single, fluid action. No more worrying about broken pieces and lost lighters.

	After using Tokeez just once, you will wonder how you ever lived without it.
With Tokeez, you toke with ease.
